{"parse":{"title":"Period (of a rhythmic light)","pageid":703,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>2-5-115</b>\n</p><p>The interval of time between the commencement of two identical successive cycles of the character of a rhythmic light. (Figs. 40-44)\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig40.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/3/30/Ch2_Fig40.jpg/100px-Ch2_Fig40.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"100\" height=\"52\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/3/30/Ch2_Fig40.jpg/150px-Ch2_Fig40.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/3/30/Ch2_Fig40.jpg/200px-Ch2_Fig40.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig41.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/3/36/Ch2_Fig41.jpg/100px-Ch2_Fig41.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"100\" height=\"39\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/3/36/Ch2_Fig41.jpg/150px-Ch2_Fig41.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/3/36/Ch2_Fig41.jpg/200px-Ch2_Fig41.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig42.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/2/2b/Ch2_Fig42.jpg/100px-Ch2_Fig42.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"100\" height=\"58\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/2/2b/Ch2_Fig42.jpg/150px-Ch2_Fig42.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/2/2b/Ch2_Fig42.jpg/200px-Ch2_Fig42.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig43.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/c/c5/Ch2_Fig43.jpg/100px-Ch2_Fig43.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"100\" height=\"32\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/c/c5/Ch2_Fig43.jpg/150px-Ch2_Fig43.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/c/c5/Ch2_Fig43.jpg/200px-Ch2_Fig43.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig44.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/e/e1/Ch2_Fig44.jpg/100px-Ch2_Fig44.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"100\" height=\"32\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/e/e1/Ch2_Fig44.jpg/150px-Ch2_Fig44.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/e/e1/Ch2_Fig44.jpg/200px-Ch2_Fig44.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><br>\n</p><p><br>\n<br>\n<i>Please note that this is the term as it stands in the original <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> Dictionary edition (1970-1989)</i>\n<br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Association of Marine Aids to Navigation and Lighthouse Authorities - AISM\n</p>\n</di